---
// src/components/ComplianceProblem.astro
const regulations = [
  { src: '/assets/CRA.svg', alt: 'CRA'},
  { src: '/assets/NIS2.svg', alt: 'NIS2'},
  { src: '/assets/DORA.svg', alt: 'DORA'},
  { src: '/assets/ISO27001.svg', alt: 'ISO 27001'},
  { src: '/assets/GDPR.svg', alt: 'GDPR'},
];
---

<section class="compliance-section">
  <div class="header">
    <h2>A perfect storm is coming</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-container">
    <div class="stats-col">
      <div class="stat-item stat-card">
        
        <div class="icons-row">
          {regulations.map(reg => (
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <img src={reg.src} alt={reg.alt} />
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p>New regulations with complex legal obligations and severe penalties</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">85%</div>
          <p>Of companies today would not pass a compliance audit <sup>[1]</sup></p>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-item stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">30%</div>
          <p>More vulnerable to cyber attacks when you're not compliant <sup>[2]</sup></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dilemma-col">
      <p class="dilemma-label">The dilemma</p>
      <h3>To be or not to be (compliant)</h3>
      
      <div class="dilemma-content">
        <p>
          To be compliant <strong class="highlight">costs time and resources</strong> 
          without generating income.
        </p>
        <p class="risk-text">
          Fail to comply means risking a fine (up to <strong class="highlight">â‚¬10 million</strong>) 
          and <strong class="highlight">being forced out of the market.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="sources">
    <p>[1] Rapporto Cyber Index PMI - ACN</p>
    <p>[2] Cost of a Data Breach Report 2023 - 2025</p>
  </footer>
</section>

<style>
  .compliance-section {
    --dilemma-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    --border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin: 4rem 0;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }
  :global(.theme-dark) .compliance-section {
    --dilemma-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    --border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .grid-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .grid-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Statistiche */
  .stats-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--dilemma-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .stat-item > p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .icons-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    padding: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .icon-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  /* Dilemma */
  .dilemma-col {
    background: var(--dilemma-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .dilemma-label { font-style: italic; opacity: 0.8; }
  
  h3 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .highlight {
    color: #ff4d6d; /* Colore d'impatto per i rischi */
  }
  
  .dilemma-content > p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .risk-text {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .sources {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .sources p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>
